reviews.text:
Light in texture, that vague hint of fizz that Fizzy sherbet brings to soda vapes, the right amount of lemon-lime to cranberry...this tastes just like my favorite holiday mixer as it's just starting to go flat. All I'm missing now is the vodka. Bear in mind, this description brought to you from the weakest of my three devices, the Dead Rabbit, so odds are you may find it far more flavorful (the one i usually run my mtl tank is on loan, so i have a pulse and one other mod, and I'm running Cardinal in the mtl tank...).&#xD;
&#xD;
Just the thing for setting off the holidays in quick, tasty fashion, or if you want something alongside your lemon flavored beverages in the summer.
